  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim is to evaluate the effect of exercise training upon endothelial function in the
      mammary artery of patients who are scheduled for CABG, as well as study the functional
      properties of single cells isolated from a small biopsy of the left ventricle obtained during
      surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
